{"tid":2171778,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"保就業益僱主 三成基層無工開","createTime":"2020-08-24T07:36:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-02T13:47:43.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"cf07f5e0a91597ac210a0780864c2372ba8a5d8c","tid":2171778,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T07:36:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200824/DIVBEZWH5RETHNTTPXDS7CEDUE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200824%2FDIVBEZWH5RETHNTTPXDS7CEDUE%2F&d=aCvg504CNSeS5FxaNurzsgDpGYGFnKQRHckm7FIFNPY%3D&h=eb3e372c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200824%2FDIVBEZWH5RETHNTTPXDS7CEDUE%2F&h=9a4cfb35\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200824/DIVBEZWH5RETHNTTPXDS7CEDUE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n保就業益僱主 三成基層無工開<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/9Gqze7RVcAaLrCBMXeKlCdKBNQc=/4992x3222/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GJCXQPBDENB4FDFAQXRBY5C4QE.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F9Gqze7RVcAaLrCBMXeKlCdKBNQc%3D%2F4992x3222%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGJCXQPBDENB4FDFAQXRBY5C4QE.JPG&h=0fb0ac63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■社協調查發現，基層5至7月失業率平均高達28.4%。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】社區組織協會本月4日至14日訪問逾330名基層人士，了解疫潮對其生計影響。政府公佈5月至7月的整體最新失業率為6.1%，就業不足率為3.5%，但社協調查發現，基層5至7月失業率平均達28.4%，最高峯更達35.1%，就業不足率平均52.3%。<br />\n<br />\n社協指逾一成基層自疫潮開始失業，迄今七個月仍未能就業，連續失業三個月以上的佔總失業人數75.6%。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n社協指，雖然政府動用近3,000億元推行防疫抗疫基金，但保就業計劃資助落了僱主袋，。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"e81cec5203a620a4315dfe34fb135c6e58dc4581","tid":2171778,"uid":54975,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T07:37:46.000Z","msg":"保僱主基金<br />\n保大財團基金<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /